    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Open frameworks of beams over a stage, below the roof but with working room between the grid and the roof, used principally for the suspension of drapery and scenery.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
